<p><b>The Chaplaincy team</b><br/> <br/>We are here to help in any way we can.<br/>• Revd Tom Gibbons<br/>• Mrs Patsy Ottewell <br/>• Revd Virginia Ramsey <br/> <br/><b>How to get in touch</b><br/>The chaplains have an office beside the Prayer Room on the main corridor. You can leave a message at the office by phoning hospital extension 5451. Urgent requests for a chaplain should be made through the hospital switchboard.<br/><br/><b>The Hospital Prayer Room</b><br/>There is an attractive room set aside for private prayer and personal reflection on the main corridor of the ground floor. The prayer room is open at all times. It is designed to be </p>
